Package: GenovisR
Type: Package
Title: Visualizing and analyzing genotypic data
Version: 0.1.3
Date: 2024-10-2
Authors@R: 
    person("Tomoyuki", "Furuta", , "f.tomoyuki@okayama-u.ac.jp", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0869-6626"))
Description: GenovisR is an R package designed for visualizing and analyzing 
    genotypic data. It provides comprehensive tools to import, visualize, 
    and summarize genotype, haplotype, and dosage data. The package also includes 
    a Shiny application for interactive data exploration.
